Source: haskell-openal
Section: haskell
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Kari Pahula <kaol@debian.org>
Standards-Version: 3.8.1
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), haddock (>= 2.4.2), hscolour, haskell-devscripts, cdbs, ghc6, ghc6-prof, ghc6-doc, libghc6-opengl-dev (>= 2.2.3.0), libghc6-opengl-prof, libghc6-opengl-doc, libopenal-dev

Package: libghc6-openal-dev
Section: haskell
Architecture: any
Depends: ${haskell:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libopenal-dev
Suggests: libghc6-openal-prof, libghc6-openal-doc
Description: Haskell OpenAL binding for GHC
 This package provides a library for the Haskell programming language.
 .
 This library provides a Haskell binding for the OpenAL cross-platform
 3D audio API, appropriate for use with gaming applications and many other
 types of audio applications.  For more information about OpenAL
 please see: <http://www.openal.org/>.

